4
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:55,050
CMD: "no if you can just back up to the entryway of that room"

5
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:59,860
CMD: "take a photo"

6
00:00:55,850 --> 00:01:00,850
CMD: "and then go into the other entryway on the left side of that room"

7
00:01:03,040 --> 00:01:08,040
CMD: "and take a photo in front and behind you"

8
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:32,920
Robot: "executing..."

9
00:02:08,010 --> 00:02:13,010
CMD: "nope stop stop"

10
00:02:15,830 --> 00:02:20,830
Robot: "Did I misunderstand?"

